l-prepared to embark on their educational journey. We believe that every student deserves access to high-quality education and the opportunity to experience diverse cultures. By partnering with top universities and leveraging our expertise,</p>','34','[{\"name\":\"LA Trobe University -  Top Agent USA 2024\",\"image\":\"182\"},{\"name\":\"National University -  Gold Agent Certificate\",\"image\":\"184\"}]','2024-11-03 04:05:43','2024-11-26 05:59:58',NULL);
